  "instructions": [
    "Combine dried dates, molasses, white granulated sugar, brown sugar, and miso paste in a blender or food processor. Blend until the mixture forms a smooth paste.",
    "Heat the sugar paste in a saucepan over medium heat, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the ginger, cinnamon, and star anise to the saucepan and continue to cook for 5 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the vinegar, water, and vegetable oil to the saucepan and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes, or until the jelly has thickened.",
    "Stir in the fresh thyme and remove from heat.",
    "Let cool slightly before transferring to a glass jar or container for serving."
  ],
